<h2>Welcome! <small>- Get update notification for your google drive -</small></h2>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span8">
<p>
  Google Drive Notifier check your Google Drive and
  send notification mail when documents updated.
</p>

<p>
  I hope Google Drive have this function, but not yet.
  So I wrote and released notifier as a web app to allow
  everyone share. Use this web app freely.
</p>

<h3>Features</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Notify via email for document updates.</li>
  <li>Configurable check target (Activity, All, Own, Starred).</li>
  <li>Configurable check interval.</li>
  <li>...just all!</li>
</ul>

<% if !user_signed_in? %>
<p class="welcome-signin">
<%= link_to 'Sign in with Google', new_user_session_path, :class => 'btn btn-large btn-primary' %>
</p>
<% end %>
  </div>
</div><!--/row-->
